descriptionHtml:
Sorry when my english is bad, it\'s not my native language
This Mod add a ring, which makes you immune to fire, frost, shock, poison, magic and diseases. It\'s located in Whiterun in front of the store Warmaiden in an Old Barrel.

.............................................................................................................................................................

Dieser Mod fügt einen Ring hinzu, der euch immun gegen Feuer, Frost, Schock, Magie, Gift und Krankheiten macht. Er befindet in Weißlauf in einem altem Fass (Old Barrel) vor der Kriegsjungfer.
author: Lokmi
